    "description": {
      "value": "<p>By 6th level, you find comfort in the forefront and have begun to hone your skills to excel there. You gain the follow benefits:</p><ul><li>You are not slowed by difficult terrain.</li><li>When you benefit from half cover treat it as though it was three-quarters cover.</li><li>You can attempt to hide even when you are only lightly obscured by terrain, natural phenomena or other creatures.</li></ul><p>Furthermore, while leading others across distances for at least 1 hour, you gain the follow benefits:</p><ul><li>Difficult terrain does not slow your group's travel.</li><li>Your group cannot become lost except by magical means.</li><li>Even when engaged in another activity while traveling (such as foraging, navigating, or tracking), your group remain alert to danger.</li></ul>",
